# Portfolio Promotion Board - 2026-06

Date: 2026-06-08

Workspace: `/opt/Axodus`

Versioning note: `/opt/Axodus` is not a Git repository. This promotion board is local/unversioned unless migrated to a versioned portfolio documentation repository.

## Board Decision Summary

Portfolio recommendation: `PORTFOLIO_READY_FOR_SELECTIVE_L4_ADVANCEMENT`

Selected next cycle: `Business L4 Consolidation`

No board decision authorizes production readiness, secrets, wallet signing, treasury movement, swaps, trading, minting, settlement, payouts, production credentials or on-chain writes.

## Promotion Board

| Nucleus | Board Decision | Current Maturity | Rationale |
|---|---|---|---|
| Core | HOLD | L5 | Keep pre-RC contractual track stable; consumer pilot and RC authority remain incomplete. |
| Governance | HOLD | L5 | High evidence, but transport/API execution, persistence, executor, treasury and on-chain authority remain blocked. |
| Documentation | HOLD | L4 Readiness | VitePress/content/governance evidence is complete enough for readiness, but publication authority/versioning remain unresolved. |
| Dex | HOLD | L4 Readiness | DEX-REQ-11 closed the technical readiness track; functional DEX evolution is paused by executive directive. |
| Business | PROMOTE | L4 Candidate | Strong validation evidence and lower immediate execution risk make Business the selected L4 consolidation target. |
| Mining | HOLD | L4 Candidate | Validation passed with warnings; payout, provider custody and treasury gates remain active. |
| Academy | HOLD | L4 Candidate | Validation passed; rewards, certification, contract deployment, minting and treasury gates remain active. |
| Marketplace | HOLD | L4 Candidate | Validation passed; value-transfer, settlement, payment, wallet, bridge and treasury risk is high. |
| ACS | HOLD | L4 Candidate | Gate passed; execution authority, credentials, Hummingbot runtime, trading and treasury remain blocked. |
| BBA-Agency | HOLD | L3 | L3 candidate evidence is sufficient; schema alignment and production claim review remain open. |
| Lottery | HOLD | L3 | L3 mock/local evidence exists; compliance, randomness, prize, payout, treasury and on-chain blockers remain high. |
| Trading | HOLD | L4 Candidate | Local Postgres E2E passed; live trading, credentials, withdrawals, production DB and treasury remain blocked. |
| Defi | HOLD | L4 Readiness | Phase 3 planning is approved as planning only; custody, staking, oracle/reconciliation and treasury gates remain blocked. |
| AxodusAPP | HOLD | L4 Readiness | Integration shell is viable, but uneven module readiness and real backend integration remain pending. |

## Selective Advancement Target

Selected target: Business

Decision: `PROMOTE`

Promotion meaning:

- advance Business into a bounded L4 consolidation cycle;
- improve persistence/billing boundary clarity;
- strengthen integration contracts;
- preserve non-production state.

Promotion does not mean:

- production billing approval;
- payment execution;
- treasury movement;
- ACS production provisioning;
- governance proposal execution;
- production readiness.

## Hold Reasons By Category

| Category | Nuclei | Reason |
|---|---|---|
| Production/execution authority | ACS, Trading, Defi, Dex, Governance | Execution-sensitive authority is not approved. |
| Value transfer/payment/payout | Marketplace, Mining, Lottery, Academy, Business | Payment, reward, payout, minting, billing or treasury gates remain active. |
| Publication/versioning | Documentation | Publication authority and versioning remain unresolved. |
| Integration symmetry | AxodusAPP, BBA-Agency | Integration coverage or schema/runtime alignment needs further evidence. |
| Pre-RC stability | Core | Core remains contractual/pre-RC and should not be expanded into runtime. |

## Board Recommendation

Proceed with `Business L4 Consolidation` as the next cycle.

The next cycle must remain evidence-backed, non-production, non-treasury, non-payment-executing and non-governance-executing.
